# Bloclance - Freelance Services Platform

## Project Overview
Bloclance is a freelance services marketplace platform built with modern tech stack.

## Tech Stack
- pnpm (package manager)
- TypeScript
- Viem
- Hardhat

## Coding Standards

### TypeScript
- Strict TypeScript usage required
- No 'any' types allowed
- Define proper interfaces and types
- Use type inference when obvious

### Testing
- Use proper testing patterns
- Maintain good test coverage

### Git Practices
- Use meaningful commit messages
- Follow conventional commits
- Create feature branches
- Review code before merging

### Documentation
- Document complex logic
- Add comments when necessary
- Keep README updated

### Security
- Implement proper authentication
- Use proper authorization
- Sanitize user inputs
- Follow security best practices

Remember, boss: This is a living document and should be updated as new standards and practices are adopted.